"To buy a printing press and other equipment and start the racket. The Arizona bluff was a nice out-of-the-way spot, so we decided to have our counterfeit checks dropped there at night. Weth-erby rigged up some electric lanterns to outline the giant so our pilot could spot the right place."\par
