"Another bright idea of Wetherby's." Purdy snorted in disgust. "He wanted a nice, innocent-looking front man and thought this Grafton would be a sucker to join us. But he wasn't-not even after Wetherby tried to frame Grafton by making him pass some bad checks.\par
